<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5363646>
    dc:description "FIGURES 100–105. Anaphothrips of Australia. (100) A. gillespiei tergites V–VII. A. glenysae 101–105: (101) meso & metanotum with forewing base; (102) head & pronotum; (103) antenna; (104) tergites V–VIII; (105) pronotum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5363646/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5314013>
    dc:description "FIGURES 92–99. Anaphothrips of Australia. (92) A. geleznowiae head & pronotum. A. gillespiei 93–99: (93) male tergite IX; (94) meso & metanotum; (95) forewing base; (96) head & pronotum; (97) antenna; (98) tergites VII–VIII; (99) male sternites." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5314013/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

